#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konsolekalendar; is a command line interface to &kde; calendars."
msgstr "&konsolekalendar; je vmesnik ukazne vrstice za &kde; koledarje."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "&package;"
msgstr "&package;"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kappname;"
msgstr "&kappname;"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "KOrganizer"
msgstr "KOrganizer"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; is a command line interface to calendars. It lets you "
"view, insert, remove, or modify calendar events by way of the command line "
"or from a scripting language. Additionally, &konsolekalendar; can create a "
"new calendar, export a calendar to a variety of other formats, and import "
"another calendar."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; je vmesnik ukazne vrstice za koledarje. Omogoča pregled, "
"vstavljanje, odstranjevanje ali spreminjanje koledarskih dogodkov prek "
"ukazne vrstice ali skriptnega jezika. Poleg tega lahko s &konsolekalendar; "
"ustvarite nov koledar, izvozite koledar v različne druge formate in uvozite "
"drug koledar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In its basic mode, &konsolekalendar; displays the list of events in your "
"default calendar for the current day (from 7:00 to 17:00)."
msgstr ""
"V osnovnem načinu &konsolekalendar; prikaže seznam dogodkov v privzetem "
"koledarju za trenutni dan (od 7:00 do 17:00)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main features of &konsolekalendar;:"
msgstr "Glavne značilnosti &konsolekalendar;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "View calendar entries from a start date/time to end date/time"
msgstr ""
"Ogled koledarskih vnosov od začetnega datuma/časa do končnega datuma/časa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert (add) calendar entries"
msgstr "Vstavi (dodaj) koledarski vnos"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove (delete) calendar entries"
msgstr "Odstrani (izbriši) vnos v koledarju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modify (change) calendar entries"
msgstr "Spremeni (zamenjaj) koledarski vnos"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new calendar"
msgstr "Ustvari novega koledarja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export calendar entries to other file formats"
msgstr "Izvozi koledarski vnos v druge oblike datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import an existing calendar"
msgstr "Uvoz obstoječega koledarja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; is <emphasis>not</emphasis> another graphical user "
"interface to a &kde; calendar (i.e. &korganizer;). &konsolekalendar; is "
"intended solely for uses where a graphical user interface is not practical "
"or possible."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; <emphasis>ni</emphasis> še en grafični uporabniški vmesnik "
"za koledar &kde; (tj. &korganizer;). &konsolekalendar; je namenjen izključno "
"za uporabo, kjer grafični uporabniški vmesnik ni praktičen ali mogoč."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; does <emphasis>not</emphasis> provide a full-featured "
"language for making queries of the user's calendar: nor is it the intention "
"of the authors to ever write such a capability. Primitive command line "
"options are provided for accessing calendar events within a consecutive "
"range of dates/time stamps."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; <emphasis>ne</emphasis> zagotavlja celovitega jezika za "
"poizvedovanje po uporabnikovem koledarju: niti ni namen avtorjev, da bi kdaj "
"napisali takšno možnost. Za dostop do koledarskih dogodkov v zaporednem "
"območju datumov/časovnih žigov so na voljo primitivne možnosti ukazne "
"vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Features"
msgstr "Značilnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter you'll learn about the main features of &konsolekalendar; "
"and how to control them using the command line parameters (remember that "
"&konsolekalendar; is not a graphical user interface; it is a command line "
"program only)."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju boste spoznali glavne funkcije programa &konsolekalendar; in "
"kako jih upravljati s parametri ukazne vrstice (ne pozabite, da "
"&konsolekalendar; ni grafični uporabniški vmesnik; je samo program za ukazno "
"vrstico)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You'll learn about inserting, deleting, and changing calendar events, and "
"how to export events to other file formats. The creation and importation of "
"calendars will also be covered in this chapter."
msgstr ""
"Spoznali boste vstavljanje, brisanje in spreminjanje koledarskih dogodkov "
"ter izvoz dogodkov v druge oblike datotek. V tem poglavju sta obravnavana "
"tudi ustvarjanje in uvoz koledarjev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing Events"
msgstr "Pregled dogodkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In its default mode, or by using the <parameter>--view</parameter> option, "
"&konsolekalendar; will list all events within the range of a specified date/"
"time."
msgstr ""
"V privzetem načinu ali z uporabo možnosti <parameter>--view</parameter> bo "
"&konsolekalendar; prikazal vse dogodke v območju določenega datuma/časa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "To view all of today's events (from 7:00 to 17:00), simply run:"
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati vse današnje dogodke (od 7:00 do 17:00), preprosto "
"zaženite:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command>\n"
"</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command>\n"
"</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this next example, we view all events for the week of August 18-22:"
msgstr ""
"V naslednjem primeru so prikazani vsi dogodki v tednu od 18. do 22. avgusta:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"view</option> <option>--date <replaceable>2016-08-18</replaceable> </option> "
"<option>--end-date <replaceable>2016-08-22</replaceable></option>\n"
"</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"view</option> <option>--date <replaceable>2016-08-18</replaceable> </option> "
"<option>--end-date <replaceable>2016-08-22</replaceable></option>\n"
"</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the next event(s) on the calendar from the current time forward:"
msgstr "Prikaži naslednje dogodke v koledarju od trenutnega časa naprej:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"next</option>\n"
"</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"next</option>\n"
"</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "To view all events for the next 5 days run:"
msgstr "Če si želite ogledati vse dogodke v naslednjih 5 dneh, zaženite:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"show-next</option> <replaceable>5</replaceable>\n"
"\n"
"</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"show-next</option> <replaceable>5</replaceable>\n"
"\n"
"</userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserting Events"
msgstr "Vstavljanje dogodkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; can insert events into a calendar or calendar resource "
"using the <parameter>--add</parameter> command line argument. Events "
"successfully inserted will be immediately shown by &kde; calendar "
"applications (like &korganizer;)."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; lahko vstavi dogodke v koledar ali koledarski vir z "
"argumentom ukazne vrstice <parameter>--add</parameter>. Uspešno vstavljeni "
"dogodki bodo takoj prikazani v &kde; koledarskih aplikacijah (kot je "
"&korganizer;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "You get a list of all calendars and their id's using:"
msgstr "Z uporabo dobite seznam vseh koledarjev in njihovih identifikatorjev:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"list-calendars</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"list-calendars</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the following example, an event starting on 2016-12-01 (December 1, 2016) "
"at 10:00 and ending at 12:00 with summary \"Doctor Visit\" will be inserted "
"into the user's calendar resource with the id 8:"
msgstr ""
"V naslednjem primeru bo dogodek, ki se začne 01.12.2016 ob 10:00 in konča ob "
"12:00 s povzetkom \"Obisk zdravnika\", vstavljen v uporabnikov koledarski "
"vir z id 8:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"add</option> <option>--calendar 8</option> <option>--date "
"<replaceable>2016-12-03</replaceable></option> <option>--time "
"<replaceable>10:00</replaceable></option> \\\n"
"<option>--end-time <replaceable>12:00</replaceable></option> <option>--"
"summary <replaceable>\"Doctor Visit\"</replaceable></option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"add</option> <option>--calendar 8</option> <option>--date "
"<replaceable>2016-12-03</replaceable></option> <option>--time "
"<replaceable>10:00</replaceable></option> \\\n"
"<option>--end-time <replaceable>12:00</replaceable></option> <option>--"
"summary <replaceable>\"Obisk zdravnika\"</replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this example, a birthday event is added into the user's calendar resource "
"with the id 8:"
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru je rojstni dan dodan v uporabnikov koledarski vir z id 8:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"add</option> <option>--calendar 8</option> <option>--date "
"<replaceable>2016-12-06</replaceable></option> <option>--summary "
"<replaceable>\"My Birthday\"</replaceable></option> \\\n"
"<option>--description <replaceable>\"Party Time\"</replaceable></option></"
"userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"add</option> <option>--calendar 8</option> <option>--date "
"<replaceable>2016-12-06</replaceable></option> <option>--summary "
"<replaceable>\"Moj rojstni dan\"</replaceable></option> \\\n"
"<option>--description <replaceable>\"Čas za zabavo\"</replaceable></option></"
"userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here a one week vacation is inserted into a calendar with the id 8:"
msgstr "Tukaj je enotedenski dopust vstavljen v koledar z id 8:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"add</option> <option>--calendar <replaceable>12</replaceable></option> "
"<option>--date <replaceable>2017-08-01</replaceable></option> \\\n"
"<option>--end-date <replaceable>2017-08-07</replaceable></option> <option>--"
"summary <replaceable>\"Vacation\"</replaceable></option> <option>--"
"description <replaceable>\"Nobody will ever find me!\"</replaceable></"
"option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"add</option> <option>--calendar <replaceable>12</replaceable></option> "
"<option>--date <replaceable>2017-08-01</replaceable></option> \\\n"
"<option>--end-date <replaceable>2017-08-07</replaceable></option> <option>--"
"summary <replaceable>\"Počitnice\"</replaceable></option> <option>--"
"description <replaceable>\"Nihče me nikoli ne bo našel!\"</replaceable></"
"option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removing Entries"
msgstr "Odstranjevanje vnosov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; supports the removal of entries in a calendar file or "
"resource using the <parameter>--delete</parameter> command line argument. "
"Calendar entries to be removed are specified exactly by their Unique-string "
"identifier (<acronym>UID</acronym>) using the <parameter>--uid</parameter> "
"option. <acronym>UIDs</acronym> are found by first viewing the event, using "
"the <parameter>--view</parameter>, <parameter>--next</parameter> or "
"<parameter>--show-next</parameter> options."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; podpira odstranjevanje vnosov v datoteki ali viru "
"koledarja z uporabo argumenta <parameter>--delete</parameter> ukazne "
"vrstice. Vnosi koledarja, ki jih je treba odstraniti, so točno določeni s "
"svojim unikatnim identifikatorjem niza (<acronym>UID</acronym>) z uporabo "
"možnosti <parameter>--uid</parameter>. <acronym>UID</acronym> se poišče "
"tako, da se najprej pogleda dogodek z uporabo možnosti <parameter>--view</"
"parameter>, <parameter>--next</parameter> ali <parameter>--show-next</"
"parameter>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Events successfully deleted will be immediately removed from within &kde; "
"calendar applications (&korganizer; for example)."
msgstr ""
"Uspešno izbrisani dogodki bodo takoj odstranjeni iz aplikacij &kde; "
"koledarja (na primer &korganizer;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you delete something from the calendar you <emphasis>cannot</emphasis> "
"undo it! In other words, when you delete an entry you cannot reverse the "
"deletion. It's gone for good."
msgstr ""
"Ko nekaj izbrišete iz koledarja, tega <emphasis>ne morete </"
"emphasis>povrniti! Z drugimi besedami, ko izbrišete vnos, izbrisa ne morete "
"razveljaviti. Za vedno je izgine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here we delete a calendar entry with <acronym>UID</acronym> "
"<replaceable>&konsolekalendar;-1887551750.196</replaceable>:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj izbrišemo koledarski vnos z <acronym>UID</acronym> "
"<replaceable>&konsolekalendar;-1887551750.196</replaceable>:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"delete</option> <option>--uid <replaceable>&konsolekalendar;-1887551750.196</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"delete</option> <option>--uid <replaceable>&konsolekalendar;-1887551750.196</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifying Entries"
msgstr "Spreminjanje vnosov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; supports the modification of existing entries in a "
"calendar file or resource using the <parameter>--change</parameter> command "
"line argument. Calendar entries to be modified are specified exactly by "
"their Unique-string identifier (<acronym>UID</acronym>) using the "
"<parameter>--uid</parameter> option. <acronym>UIDs</acronym> are found by "
"first viewing the event, using the <parameter>--view</parameter>, "
"<parameter>--next</parameter> or <parameter>--show-next</parameter> options."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; podpira spreminjanje obstoječih vnosov v datoteki ali viru "
"koledarja z uporabo argumenta ukazne vrstice <parameter>--change</"
"parameter>. Vnosi koledarja, ki jih je treba spremeniti, so točno določeni s "
"svojim unikatnim identifikatorjem niza<acronym>UID</acronym>) z uporabo "
"možnosti <parameter>--uid</parameter>. <acronym>UID</acronym> se poiščejo "
"tako, da se najprej pregleda dogodek z uporabo možnosti <parameter>--view</"
"parameter>, <parameter>--next</parameter> ali <parameter>--show-next</"
"parameter>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing behaves in the same way as inserting: you can change an event's "
"start date and time, end date and time, summary, location, and description. "
"Events successfully changed will be immediately shown modified within &kde; "
"calendar applications (&korganizer;)."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje poteka enako kot vstavljanje: spremenite lahko datum in čas "
"začetka dogodka, datum in čas konca, povzetek, lokacijo in opis. Uspešno "
"spremenjeni dogodki se takoj prikažejo spremenjeni v &kde; aplikacijah "
"koledarja (&korganizer;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Example:</emphasis> Here we change the summary and description of "
"a calendar entry with <acronym>UID</acronym> "
"<replaceable>&konsolekalendar;-1887551750.196</replaceable>:"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Primer:</emphasis> Tukaj spremenimo povzetek in opis koledarskega "
"vnosa z <acronym>UID</acronym> "
"<replaceable>&konsolekalendar;-1887551750.196</replaceable>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"change</option> <option>--uid <replaceable>&konsolekalendar;-1887551750.196</"
"replaceable></option> <option>--summary <replaceable>\"Get my head examined"
"\"</replaceable></option> <option>--description <replaceable>\"don't go to "
"that doctor anymore!\"</replaceable></option> </userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"change</option> <option>--uid <replaceable>&konsolekalendar;-1887551750.196</"
"replaceable></option> <option>--summary <replaceable>\"Preglejte mi glavo\"</"
"replaceable></option> <option>--description <replaceable>\"ne hodi več k "
"temu zdravniku!\"</replaceable></option> </userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a New Calendar File"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje nove datoteke koledarja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; can be used to create new calendars from existing files. "
"You can create the calendar using the option <option>--create</option> with "
"the filename as argument. The file must be a valid <acronym>iCal</acronym> "
"or <acronym>vCal</acronym> file."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; lahko uporabite za ustvarjanje novih koledarjev iz "
"obstoječih datotek. Koledar lahko ustvarite z možnostjo <option>--create</"
"option> z imenom datoteke kot argumentom. Datoteka mora biti veljavna "
"datoteka <acronym>iCal</acronym> ali <acronym>vCal</acronym>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: You can not use the option <option>--dry-run</option> to test if the "
"resource can be created."
msgstr ""
"Opomba: Da preverite, ali je vir mogoče ustvariti Ne morete uporabiti "
"možnosti -<option>--dry-run</option>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: &konsolekalendar; needs the file to work, so never delete the file by "
"hand."
msgstr ""
"Opomba: &konsolekalendar; zahteva, da datoteka deluje, zato datoteke nikoli "
"ne izbrišite ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Technical sidenote: &konsolekalendar; creates with this command a new "
"<acronym>Akonadi</acronym> resource pointing to this file. It does not "
"prevent you to create multiple resources pointing to the same file."
msgstr ""
"Tehnična opomba: &konsolekalendar; s tem ukazom ustvari nov vir "
"<acronym>Akonadi</acronym>, ki kaže na to datoteko. Ne preprečuje "
"ustvarjanja več virov, ki kažejo na isto datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new calendar from an existing file named "
"<filename><replaceable>vacation.ics</replaceable></filename>:"
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite nov koledar iz obstoječe datoteke z imenom "
"<filename><replaceable>počitnice.ics</replaceable></filename>:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"create</option> <option><replaceable>vacation.ics</replaceable></option></"
"userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>Konsolekalendar</command> -<option>--"
"create</option> <option><replaceable>počitnice.ics</replaceable></option></"
"userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The resource will be named <quote>vacation</quote> using <option>--list-"
"calendars</option>"
msgstr ""
"Vir bo poimenovan <quote>počitnice</quote> z uporabo -<option>--list-"
"calendars</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is not possible to delete an <acronym>Akonadi</acronym> resource with "
"&konsolekalendar;, you have to use &korganizer; or "
"<application>akonadiconsole</application>."
msgstr ""
"Vira <acronym>Akonadi</acronym> ni mogoče izbrisati s &konsolekalendar;, "
"uporabiti morate &korganizer; ali <application>akonadiconsole</application>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting to Other Formats"
msgstr "Izvoz v druge formate"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; can export a calendar to other well known formats. "
"Exporting is a special form of viewing. By default, events are viewed in "
"<quote>&konsolekalendar; text</quote> format. To change the viewing format "
"use the <parameter>--export-type</parameter> command line argument."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; lahko izvozi koledar v druge dobro znane formate. Izvoz je "
"posebna oblika gledanja. Dogodki so privzeto prikazani v <quote>obliki "
"&konsolekalendar; besedilo</quote>. Če želite spremeniti obliko ogleda, "
"uporabite argument ukazne vrstice <parameter>--export-type</parameter>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see a list of all supported export formats, use the <parameter>--export-"
"list</parameter> option, as in:"
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati seznam vseh podprtih oblik izvoza, uporabite možnost "
"<parameter>--export-list</parameter>, kot v:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"export-list</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"export-list</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export Formats"
msgstr "Izvozne oblike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some, but not necessarily all, of the supported formats are described in the "
"this section."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere, vendar ne nujno vse, podprte oblike zapisa so opisane v tem "
"razdelku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konsolekalendar; Text Format"
msgstr "&konsolekalendar; Oblika besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; Text Format is &konsolekalendar;'s native format and is "
"designed to be comfortable to read and to be parsed by follow-on scripts."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; Oblika besedila je izvorna oblika &konsolekalendar; in je "
"zasnovana tako, da je udobna za branje in razčlenjena z nadaljnjimi skripti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &konsolekalendar; Text Format is:"
msgstr "Oblika besedila &konsolekalendar; je:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Date:\\t&lt;Incidence Date&gt;(dddd yyyy-MM-dd)\n"
"[\\t&lt;Incidence Start Time&gt;(hh:mm) - &lt;Incidence End Time&gt;(hh:"
"mm)]\n"
"Summary:\n"
"\\t&lt;Incidence Summary | \"(no summary available)\"&gt;\n"
"Location:\n"
"\\t&lt;Incidence Location | \"(no location available)\"&gt;\n"
"Description:\n"
"\\t&lt;Incidence Description | \"(no description available)\"&gt;\n"
"UID:\n"
"\\t&lt;Incidence UID&gt;\n"
"--------------------------------------------------"
msgstr ""
"Datum:\\t&lt;Incidenčni datum&gt;(dddd yyyy-MM-dd)\n"
"[\\t&lt;Incidenčni začetni čas&gt;(hh:mm) - &lt;Incidenčni končni čas&gt;(hh:"
"mm)]\n"
"Povzetek:\n"
"\\t&lt;Incidenčni povzetek | \"(povzetek ni na voljo)\"&gt;\n"
"Lokacija:\n"
"\\t&lt;Incidenčna lokacija | \"(lokacija ni na voljo)\"&gt;\n"
"Opis:\n"
"\\t&lt;Incidenčni opis | \"(opis ni na voljo)\"&gt;\n"
"UID:\n"
"\\t&lt;incidenčni UID&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Output of <userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--next</"
"option> <option>--export-type</option> <option>Text</option></userinput>:"
msgstr ""
"Izhod <userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> --next <option>--export-"
"type</option> <option></option> <option>Besedilo</option></userinput>:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Date:   Tuesday 2016-11-29\n"
"        08:00 - 09:00\n"
"Summary:\n"
"        Staff Meeting\n"
"Location:\n"
"        Conference Room\n"
"Description:\n"
"        Meet with the entire staff to discuss the project.\n"
"UID:\n"
"        &konsolekalendar;-1924621834.134\n"
"--------------------------------------------------"
msgstr ""
"Datum:   Torek 2016-11-29\n"
"        08:00 - 09:00\n"
"Povzetek:\n"
"        Sestanek osebja\n"
"Lokacija:\n"
"        Konferenčna soba\n"
"Opis:\n"
"        Sestani se s celotnim osebjem, da se pogovorimo o projektu.\n"
"UID:\n"
"        &konsolekalendar;-1924621834.134\n"
"--------------------------------------------------"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konsolekalendar; Short Text Format"
msgstr "&konsolekalendar; Oblika kratkega besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Short Text Format provides a more compact, less verbose version of "
"&konsolekalendar;'s native format."
msgstr ""
"Oblika kratkega besedila zagotavlja bolj kompaktno, manj besedno različico "
"izvorne oblike &konsolekalendar;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &konsolekalendar; Short Text Format is:"
msgstr "&konsolekalendar; oblika kratkega besedila je:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[--------------------------------------------------]\n"
"{&lt;Incidence Date&gt;(dddd yyyy-MM-dd)]\n"
"[&lt;Incidence Start Time&gt;(hh:mm) - &lt;Incidence End Time&gt;(hh:mm) | "
"\"\\t\"]\n"
"\\t&lt;Incidence Summary | \\t&gt;[, &lt;Incidence Location&gt;]\n"
"\\t\\t&lt;Incidence Description | \"\\t\"&gt;"
msgstr ""
"[--------------------------------------------------]\n"
"{&lt;Incidenčni datum&gt;(dddd yyyy-MM-dd)]\n"
"[&lt;Incidenčni začetni čas&gt;(hh:mm) - &lt;Incidenčni končni čas&gt;(hh:"
"mm) | \"\\t\"]\n"
"\\t&lt;Incidenčni povzetek | \\t&gt;[, &lt;Incidenčna lokacija&gt;]\n"
"\\t\\t&lt;Incidenčni opis | \"\\t\"&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Output of <userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--next</"
"option> <option>--export-type</option> <option>Short</option></userinput>:"
msgstr ""
"Izpis <userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--next</option> "
"<option>--export-type</option> <option>Short</option></userinput>:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"--------------------------------------------------\n"
"Tuesday 2016-11-29\n"
"08:00 - 09:00   Staff Meeting, Conference Room\n"
"                Meet with the entire staff to discuss the project."
msgstr ""
"--------------------------------------------------\n"
"Torek 2016-11-29\n"
"08:00 - 09:00   Sestanek z osebjem, Konferenčna soba\n"
"                Sestani se s celotnim osebjem, da se pogovorimo o projektu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comma-Separated Values (<acronym>CSV</acronym>) Format"
msgstr "Oblika zapisa vrednosti, ločenih z vejico (<acronym>CSV)</acronym>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Comma-Separated Value Format displays the event values in the same order as "
"&konsolekalendar; Text format. The only difference is that all the "
"information is on the same row with each field separated by a comma. The "
"resulting exported files can be imported directly into spreadsheet programs "
"like &calligrasheets;, <application>OpenOffice.org Calc</application>, and "
"<application>&Microsoft; Excel</application>. Also, <acronym>CSV</acronym> "
"format is easy to parse with follow-on scripts."
msgstr ""
"Oblika: Vrednosti, ločene z vejico, prikaže vrednosti dogodka v enakem "
"vrstnem redu kot &konsolekalendar; Besedilna oblika. Edina razlika je, da so "
"vse informacije v isti vrstici, pri čemer je vsako polje ločeno z vejico. "
"Nastale izvožene datoteke lahko uvozite neposredno v programe za "
"preglednice, kot so &calligrasheets;, <application>OpenOffice.org Calc</"
"application> in <application>&Microsoft; Excel</application>. Tudi format "
"<acronym>CSV</acronym> je enostavno razčleniti z nadaljnjimi skripti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Comma-Separated Value (<acronym>CSV</acronym>) format is:"
msgstr "Oblika vrednosti, ločenih z vejico (<acronym>CSV</acronym>), je:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\"Weekday, Month Day, Year\",\"HH:MM\",\"Weekday, Month Day, Year\",\"HH:MM"
"\",\"Summary\",\"Location\",\"Description\",\"UID\""
msgstr ""
"\"Dan v tednu, dan v mesecu, leto\", \"HH:MM\", \"Dan v tednu, dan v mesecu, "
"leto\", \"HH:MM\", \"Povzetek\", \"Lokacija\", \"Opis\", \"UID\""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Output of <userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--next</"
"option> <option>--export-type</option> <option>CSV</option></userinput>:"
msgstr ""
"Izpis <userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--next</option> "
"<option>--export-type</option> <option>CSV</option></userinput>:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\"Tuesday, November 29, 2016\",\"08:00\",\"Tuesday, November 29, 2016\","
"\"09:00\",\"Staff Meeting\",\"Conference Room\",\"Meet in the big conference "
"\\\n"
"room with the entire staff.\",\"&konsolekalendar;-1924621834.134\""
msgstr ""
"\"Torek, 29. november 2016\", \"08:00\", \"Torek, November 29, 2016\", "
"\"09:00\", \"Sestanek osebja\", \"Konferenčna soba\", \"Sestanek v veliki "
"konferenčni \\\n"
"soba s celotnim osebjem.\",\"&konsolekalendar;-1924621834.134\""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Calendars"
msgstr "Uvažanje koledarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; can import an iCal or vCal calendar file into calendar. "
"All events from the calendar being imported from will be inserted, skipping "
"identical events, that are already part of the calendar."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; v koledar lahko uvozi koledarsko datoteko iCal ali vCal. "
"Vstavljeni bodo vsi dogodki iz koledarja, iz katerega se uvažajo, pri čemer "
"bodo preskočeni enaki dogodki, ki so že del koledarja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To import calendar file <replaceable>vacation.ics</replaceable> into "
"calendar with the id <replaceable>8</replaceable> run:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite uvoziti <replaceable>počitnice.ics</replaceable> v koledarju.ics v "
"koledar z zagonom id-ja <replaceable> 8</replaceable>:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"import <replaceable>vacation.ics</replaceable></option> <option>--calendar "
"<replaceable>8</replaceable></option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput> <command>konsolekalendar</command> <option>--"
"import <replaceable>počitnice.ics</replaceable></option> <option>--calendar "
"<replaceable>8</replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Arguments"
msgstr "Argumenti ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konsolekalendar; supports the following options:"
msgstr "&konsolekalendar; podpira naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option"
msgstr "Možnost"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic options:"
msgstr "Splošne možnosti:"

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "--help, --help-all"
msgstr "--help, --help-all"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows help about the program options."
msgstr "Prikaže pomoč o možnostih programa."

# Prevod (" --something " ) ukazov?
#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "--author"
msgstr "--author"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the program author information."
msgstr "Prikaže informacije o avtorju programa."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --version"
msgstr "-v, --version"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the program version information."
msgstr "Prikaže informacije o različici programa."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "--license"
msgstr "--license"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the program license information."
msgstr "Prikaže informacije o licenci programa."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options:"
msgstr "Možnosti:"

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "--verbose"
msgstr "--verbose"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print helpful runtime messages."
msgstr "Natisni koristna sporočila v času izvajanja."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "--dry-run"
msgstr "--dry-run"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Print what would have been done, but do not execute. Do not change any "
"files; do not insert, remove, modify any existing files, nor create any new "
"files."
msgstr ""
"Natisni, kar bi bilo treba storiti, vendar ne izvedit. Ne spreminjajte "
"nobenih datotek; ne vstavljajte, odstranjujte, spreminjajte obstoječih "
"datotek in ne ustvarjajte novih datotek."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "--allow-gui"
msgstr "--allow-gui"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Permit resources which might need an interactive user interface. In normal "
"operation, only resources which never will require a user interface are used "
"(like file-based calendars)."
msgstr ""
"Dovolite vire, ki morda potrebujejo interaktivni uporabniški vmesnik. Pri "
"običajnem delovanju se uporabljajo samo viri, ki nikoli ne bodo potrebovali "
"uporabniškega vmesnika (na primer datotečni koledarji)."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Incidence types (these options can be combined):"
msgstr "Vrste pojavov (te možnosti je mogoče kombinirati):"

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "--event"
msgstr "--event"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operate for Events only (Default)."
msgstr "Deluj samo za dogodke (privzeto)."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "--todo"
msgstr "--todo"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operate for Todos only. (Not implemented)"
msgstr "Delujte samo za Todo-je. (Ni izvedeno)"

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "--journal"
msgstr "--journal"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operate for Journals only. (Not implemented)"
msgstr "Deluj samo za dnevnike. (Ni izvedeno)"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "Major Operation Modes:"
msgstr "Glavni načini delovanja:"

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "--view"
msgstr "--view"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print calendar events in specified export format."
msgstr "Natisni koledarske dogodke v izbranem formatu za izvoz."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "--add"
msgstr "--add"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert an event into the calendar."
msgstr "V koledar vstavite dogodek."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "--change"
msgstr "--change"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modify an existing calendar event."
msgstr "Spremeni obstoječ dogodek v koledarju."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "--delete"
msgstr "--delete"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove an existing calendar event."
msgstr "Odstrani obstoječi koledarski dogodek."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--create</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;filename</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--create</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;filename</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new calendar from existing file."
msgstr "Ustvarite nov koledar iz obstoječe datoteke."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--import</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;import-file</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--import</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;import-file</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import this calendar to the main calendar."
msgstr "Uvozi ta koledar v glavni koledar."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid "--list-calendars"
msgstr "--list-calendars"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "List available calendars."
msgstr "Seznam razpoložljivih koledarjev."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operation modifiers:"
msgstr "Modifikatorji delovanja:"

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid "--all"
msgstr "--all"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid "View all calendar entries."
msgstr "Pogled vseh vnosov v koledarju."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "--next"
msgstr "--next"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid "View next activity in calendar."
msgstr "Pogled naslednje dejavnosti v koledarju."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--show-next</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;days</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--show-next</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;days</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting at specified date show next # days' activities."
msgstr "Od določenega datuma naprej prikaži dejavnosti za naslednjih # dni."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--uid</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;UID</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--uid</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;UID</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "View, delete, or change the event with this Unique-string IDentifier."
msgstr ""
"Pogled, brisanje ali spreminjanje dogodka s tem enoličnim nizom "
"identifikatorja."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--date</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;date</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--date</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;date</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start at this day [YYYY-MM-DD]. Default date is Today"
msgstr "Začni na ta dan [YYYY-MM-DD]. Privzeti datum je Danes"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--time</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;time</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--time</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;time</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start at this time [HH:MM]. Default time for viewing is 07:00."
msgstr "Začetek ob tej uri [HH:MM]. Privzeta ura za ogled je 07:00."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:552 index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add or change a floating event, use the <option>--time float</option> or "
"the <option>--end-time float</option> options."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati ali spremeniti plavajoči dogodek, uporabite možnosti "
"<option>--time float</option> ali <option>--end-time float</option>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--end-date</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;end-date</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--end-date</option> <replaceable>&nbsp;end-date</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"End at this day [YYYY-MM-DD]. Default is set by <option>--date</option>."
msgstr ""
"Konec na ta dan [YYYY-MM-DD]. Privzeto je nastavljeno z <option>--date</"
