#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid "What configuration files does &konsolekalendar; use?"
msgstr "Katere konfiguracijske datoteke uporablja &konsolekalendar;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "None."
msgstr "Nobene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid "What are the application names of &konsolekalendar;?"
msgstr "Kakšna so imena aplikacij za &konsolekalendar;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar;'s application name is <application>konsolekalendar</"
"application>."
msgstr ""
"Ime aplikacije &konsolekalendar; je <application>konsolekalendar</"
"application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is the date specification format?"
msgstr "Kakšen je format specifikacije datuma?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; will reject dates specified on the command line unless "
"they are specified according to ISO 8601 standards, namely: YYYY-MM-DD. "
"Where YYYY represents a four-digit year (like 2003), MM represents a two-"
"digit month (01,02,..,12), and DD represents a two-digit day (01,02,...,31)."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; zavrne datume, ki so navedeni v ukazni vrstici, razen če "
"so navedeni v skladu s standardi ISO 8601, in sicer: YYYY-MM-DD. Pri čemer "
"je YYYY štirimestno leto (na primer 2003), MM dvomestni mesec (01,02,...12) "
"in DD dvomestni dan (01,02,...31)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; always exports dates according to the ISO 8601 format."
msgstr "&konsolekalendar; vedno izvozi datume v skladu z obliko ISO 8601."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is the time specification format?"
msgstr "Kakšen je format časovne specifikacije?"

# ISO 8601
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; will reject times specified on the command line unless "
"they are specified according to ISO 8601 standards, namely: HH:MM:SS. Where "
"HH represents a two-digit hour (01,02,...,24), MM represents a two-digit "
"minute (01,02,..,60), and SS represents a two-digit second (01,02,...,60)."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; zavrne čase, ki so navedeni v ukazni vrstici, razen če so "
"navedeni v skladu s standardi ISO 8601, in sicer: HH:MM:SS. Pri čemer HH "
"predstavlja dvomestno uro (01,02,...,24), MM predstavlja dvomestno minuto "
"(01,02,...,60) in SS predstavlja dvomestno sekundo (01,02,...,60)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; always exports times according to the ISO 8601 format."
msgstr "&konsolekalendar; vedno izvaža čase v skladu z obliko ISO 8601."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will &konsolekalendar; insert a new event that is identical to one that "
"already exists in the calendar?"
msgstr ""
"Ali bo &konsolekalendar; vstavil nov dogodek, ki je enak dogodku, ki že "
"obstaja v koledarju?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. See next question."
msgstr "Ne. Glejte naslednje vprašanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How does &konsolekalendar; determine if an event is identical to one that "
"already exists in the calendar?"
msgstr ""
"Kako &konsolekalendar; ugotovi, ali je dogodek enak dogodku, ki že obstaja v "
"koledarju?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsolekalendar; checks the specified start date and time, end date and "
"time, and summary against all events in the calendar. An event match is "
"determined if all three values match to an existing event."
msgstr ""
"&konsolekalendar; preveri navedeni začetni datum in čas, končni datum in čas "
"ter povzetek glede na vse dogodke v koledarju. Dogodek se ujema, če se vse "
"tri vrednosti ujemajo z obstoječim dogodkom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can a non-floating event be changed to a floating event?"
msgstr ""
"Ali je mogoče dogodek, ki ni spremenljiv, spremeniti v spremenljiv dogodek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. Use the <option>--time float</option> option with <option>--change</"
"option>."
msgstr ""
"Da. Uporabite <option>--time float</option> možnost z <option>--change</"
"option>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why are event <acronym>UIDs</acronym> printed in most export formats?"
msgstr ""
"Zakaj so <acronym>UID-i</acronym> dogodkov natisnjeni v večini izvoznih "
"formatov?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because you need to specify <acronym>UIDs</acronym> to delete or change "
"events. If you do not want to see event <acronym>UIDs</acronym> then use the "
"<emphasis>short</emphasis> export type (<option>--export-type short</"
"option>)."
msgstr ""
"Ker morate za brisanje ali spreminjanje dogodkov določiti <acronym>UID</"
"acronym>. Če ne želite prikazati <acronym>UID</acronym> dogodkov, uporabite "
"vrsto izvoza <emphasis>short</emphasis> (<option>--export-type short</"
"option>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I have my question added to this <acronym>FAQ</acronym>?"
msgstr "Kako lahko svoje vprašanje dodam v ta <acronym>FAQ</acronym>?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send your questions to <email>winter@kde.org</email>."
msgstr "Vprašanja pošljite na <email>winter@kde.org</email>."

